OL,7,FWarning: this article contains details
OL,8,Fthat some readers might find
OL,9,Fdistressing
OL,11,FA mother from Derbyshire says she is
OL,12,Fliving in fear after her abusive ex-
OL,13,Fpartner was released from prison,
OL,14,Fhaving served just a third of his
OL,15,Fsentence.
OL,17,FHayley Johns's former partner Matthew
OL,18,FKowal was jailed for three years for
OL,19,Fcausing actual bodily harm and common
OL,20,Fassault.
