OL,4,Cabusive ex-partner's early prison
OL,5,Crelease
OL,7,FHe was released after serving less
OL,8,Fthan three hundred days behind bars.
OL,10,FHayley from Little Eaton near Derby,
OL,11,Fsaid Kowal's abusive behaviour began
OL,12,Fjust months after they got together in
OL,13,FMay 2020.
OL,15,FHayley said she confronted him on New
OL,16,FYear's Eve when she saw he had sent
OL,17,Fintimate pictures of himself to
OL,18,Fanother woman.
OL,20,FShe said: "He went from this
OL,21,Fbeautiful, lovely man to this monster.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/11
