OL,5,Crelease
OL,7,F"He strangled me, he threw me across
OL,8,Fthe bed, he shoved sex toys in my
OL,9,Fmouth to try to shut me up."
OL,11,FAfter that first incident, his abusive
OL,12,Fbehaviour "never really stopped."
OL,14,FShe said: "It was everything I'd ever
OL,15,Fwanted, and I really really loved him.
OL,17,F"The beautiful side of him when I met
OL,18,Fhim was so infectious, but he could
OL,19,Fonly ever go a few months without
OL,20,Fcheating on me, physically and
OL,21,Fpsychologically abusing me.
