OL,5,Crelease
OL,7,F"He would flip from being nice to
OL,8,Fbeing horrible; I was always walking
OL,9,Fon eggshells."
OL,11,FHayley described how she once tried to
OL,12,Fjump out of the window after Kowal
OL,13,Fbarricaded her in her bedroom, and
OL,14,Fsaid she wanted to end her life.
OL,16,F"As a victim you're just invisible"
OL,18,FHayley said despite the abuse she
OL,19,Fsuffered, she would have taken him
OL,20,Fback if he had taken accountability
OL,21,Ffor his actions.
