OL,7,FInstead, Kowal denied some of the
OL,8,Foffences and took the case to trial,
OL,9,Fmeaning Hayley had to give evidence
OL,10,Fand be cross-examined by his barrister.
OL,12,FShe said: "The whole court experience
OL,13,Fand the aftermath has been mentally
OL,14,Fshattering for me, because he didn't
OL,15,Fget what he should have got.
OL,17,F"Even though he got the three years, I
OL,18,Fthought 'I've got some time to work on
OL,19,Fmy mental health', to try to be in a
OL,20,Fmentally stable position when he is
OL,21,Freleased.
