OL,7,FBefore Kowal was released, Hayley was
OL,8,Fgiven an indoor alarm system which
OL,9,Fwould call police directly if there is
OL,10,Fan intruder.
OL,12,FHis early release comes under
OL,13,Fgovernment plans to ease overcrowding
OL,14,Fin prisons.
OL,16,FHe will now have to wear an electronic
OL,17,Ftag and keep to a strict curfew,
OL,18,Fsomething which Hayley said is no
OL,19,Fconsolation.
