OL,5,Crelease
OL,7,FShe said: "Why are we the ones
OL,8,Fseemingly being punished and having to
OL,9,Flive in fear?"
OL,11,F"I didn't ask him to do this to me, as
OL,12,Fmany other victims didn't ask to be a
OL,13,Fvictim.
OL,15,F"I just hope me doing this will give
OL,16,Fpeople the strength to know that there
OL,17,Freally is some form of light at the
OL,18,Fend of the tunnel.
OL,20,F"It may be a long way off and it may
OL,21,Fbe a battle but you can do it."
